The  Voice Communication Specialist,  will use knowledge of Cisco Voice and Networking Technologies to ensure the successful delivery of VOIP solutions to our Agency. The candidate  will be an integral part of our Telecommunications team, collaborating internally and externally, managing a large Cisco Voice infrastructure across various facilities on Rikers, Headquarters and our Borough commands.

