- Strong familiarity with cybersecurity framework(s) (NIST, SANS, PCI, ISO 27001/27002, or CIS);
- Experience in implementation of cybersecurity policies and standards and tracking compliance with them;
- Strong investigative and analytical skills;
- Excellent oral and written communication skills, including the ability to explain complex audit issues in plain language;
